# Website Conventions

## Path Alias

- `@/*` maps to `./src/*` (e.g. `import { X } from "@/lib/firebase/admin"`)

## API Routes

- API routes live in `src/app/api/`
- Use lazy Stripe initialization (`getStripe()`) to avoid build-time env errors — never `new Stripe(...)` at module top level

## Server vs Client Components

- Prefer Server Components (default). Add `"use client"` only when needed (hooks, event handlers, browser APIs).
- Do not export `metadata` from Client Components — metadata is Server-only.

## Scripts

- `scripts/` folder is excluded from the build. Use for standalone migration scripts (e.g. `npx tsx scripts/sync-premium-users.ts`).

## Environment

- Copy root `.env` into `website/.env` or `website/.env.local` for local development.
